name: Di-Soric Connection Cable- VKHM-Z-5/4
products_description:
Unbox Industry presents connection cable by di-soric. Our open-ended connection cables are the optimal solution for putting all sensors, lighting as well as Vision and ID products into operation. They feature a stable metal union nut, good insulation properties and a high protection class.

Features:
- Drag chain compatible
- Sturdy metal union nut
- Durable PU coating
- Flexible lead design
- Good stripping properties
- High protection type
- Gold-plated plug-in contacts
